    "### 1.3 Data Summary and Initial Observations\n",
    "\n",
    "The `.info()` and `.describe()` functions are used to understand the structure and quality of the datasets.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Purpose:**\n",
    "\n",
    "- examine the column names and ensure consistency between training and testing datasets  \n",
    "- check data types of each feature  \n",
    "- identify missing values using non-null counts  \n",
    "- understand the distribution of numerical variables using summary statistics  \n",
    "- find any potential data quality issues before preprocessing  \n",
    "\n",
    "**Observations:**\n",
