   "source": [
    "## 3. Data Preparation for Modelling"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "8513ea2a",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 3.1 Feature Engineering\n",
    "\n",
    "**Purpose:**\n",
    "\n",
    "- To create new features from existing variables to improve model performance.\n",
    "- To capture hidden relationships between variables that are not directly visible in raw data.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Observations:**\n",
    "\n",
    "- Three new features were created:\n",
    "    - Tank_Shape_Ratio:\n",
    "        - represents the physical shape of the tank (width vs length)\n",
    "        - captures geometric variation, which may influence pressure behaviour\n",
    "    - Vapour_Ratio:\n",
    "        - shows how much of the tank is occupied by vapour\n",
    "        - as vapour proportion directly affects explosion pressure\n",
    "    - Temp_Difference - \n",
    "        - captures the difference between vapour and liquid temperatures\n",
    "        - captures thermal imbalance which is highly relevant for pressure prediction and likely to be a strong predictor\n",
    "\n",
    "**From summary statistics:**\n",
    "1. Tank_Shape_Ratio\n",
    "- Mean ≈ 0.47: tanks are longer than they are wide\n",
    "- Range: 0.04 to 4.17: some tanks are extremely narrow or wide\n",
    "\n",
    "2. Vapour_Ratio\n",
    "- Mean ≈ 0.53: roughly half the tank is vapour on average\n",
    "- Range: 0.08 to 1.10: mostly realistic proportions\n",
    "\n",
    "3. Temp_Difference\n",
    "- Mean ≈ 55K: vapour is generally hotter than liquid\n",
    "- Range: -140 to 246: wide variation"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 29,
   "id": "b0b9e21a",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Core Ratio Features\n",
    "\n",
    "train_df['Tank_Shape_Ratio'] = train_df['Tank Width (m)'] / (train_df['Tank Length (m)'] + 1e-6)\n",
    "train_df['Vapour_Ratio'] = train_df['Vapour Height (m)'] / (train_df['Tank Height (m)'] + 1e-6)\n",
    "train_df['Obstacle_Size_Ratio'] = train_df['Obstacle Width (m)'] / (train_df['Tank Width (m)'] + 1e-6)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Temperature Features\n",
    "\n",
    "train_df['Temp_Difference'] = train_df['Vapour Temperature (K)'] - train_df['Liquid Temperature (K)']\n",
    "train_df['Temp_Ratio'] = train_df['Vapour Temperature (K)'] / (train_df['Liquid Temperature (K)'] + 1e-6)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Volume Features \n",
    "\n",
    "train_df['Tank_Volume'] = (\n",
    "    train_df['Tank Length (m)'] *\n",
    "    train_df['Tank Width (m)'] *\n",
    "    train_df['Tank Height (m)']\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "train_df['Vapour_Volume'] = (\n",
    "    train_df['Tank Length (m)'] *\n",
    "    train_df['Tank Width (m)'] *\n",
    "    train_df['Vapour Height (m)']\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Non-linear boost\n",
    "train_df['Vapour_Volume_Sq'] = train_df['Vapour_Volume'] ** 2\n",
    "\n",
    "# Sensor Position Features \n",
    "\n",
    "train_df['Sensor_Distance'] = np.sqrt(\n",
    "    train_df['Sensor Position x']**2 +\n",
    "    train_df['Sensor Position y']**2 +\n",
    "    train_df['Sensor Position z']**2\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "train_df['Sensor_Distance_Sq'] = train_df['Sensor_Distance'] ** 2\n",
    "\n",
    "train_df['Sensor_Height_Ratio'] = train_df['Sensor Position z'] / (train_df['Tank Height (m)'] + 1e-6)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Relative position inside vapour\n",
    "train_df['Sensor_to_Vapour'] = (\n",
    "    train_df['Vapour Height (m)'] - train_df['Sensor Position z']\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Normalized distance\n",
    "train_df['Distance_Normalized'] = train_df['Sensor_Distance'] / (train_df['Tank Height (m)'] + 1e-6)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Smart Interaction Features\n",
    "\n",
    "train_df['Temp_Vapour_Interaction'] = train_df['Temp_Difference'] * train_df['Vapour_Ratio']\n",
    "\n",
    "# Relative position feature (NEW - HIGH VALUE)\n",
    "\n",
    "train_df['Vapour_Liquid_Ratio'] = (\n",
    "    train_df['Vapour Height (m)'] / (train_df['Liquid Ratio'] + 1e-6)\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "train_df['Relative_Sensor_Position'] = (\n",
    "    train_df['Sensor Position z'] / (train_df['Vapour Height (m)'] + 1e-6)\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "train_df['Distance_from_Vapour'] = abs(\n",
    "    train_df['Sensor Position z'] - train_df['Vapour Height (m)']\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "train_df['Log_Vapour_Volume'] = np.log1p(train_df['Vapour_Volume'])\n",
    "train_df['Log_Sensor_Distance'] = np.log1p(train_df['Sensor_Distance'])"
   ]
  },
  {
