    "\n",
    "**Purpose:**\n",
    "\n",
    "- 80–20 split is used, where 80% of the data is used for training and 20% for validation\n",
    "\n",
    "**Observations:**\n",
    "\n",
    "- Training set contains 7992 observations  \n",
    "- Validation set contains 1998 observations  \n",
    "- The split ensures that:\n",
    "  - the model is trained on sufficient data  \n",
    "  - performance is evaluated on unseen data  "
